videos.author: MTGGoldfish
videos.title: Magic Mechanics That Are Never Coming Back
videos.description:
One thing that Wizards does regularly is bring back old mechanics in new sets. Today we look at the Magic: the Gathering mechanics that are least likely to ever make a return!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
